{"type": "article", "id": 21680, "title": "一个油漆刷品牌应该怎么做广告？", "description": "当然是好好地刷墙。", "date": "2016-02-02T08:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 5409, "name": "户外广告"}, {"id": 22978, "name": "OBI"}, {"id": 22979, "name": "Sherwin-Williams"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 101, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607105025XR2Lh31eIatTvS9q.png", "contents": "\n\n<div>擅长刷墙的涂具公司，不把户外广告做得好看些好像说不过去。创意公司 Deutsch 为 Sherwin-Williams 旗下油漆刷品牌 Purdy 设计了两个户外广告，一个是将你眼睛里看到的一切都刷上油漆。 </div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105017vaO28IbfFZ596KD1.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55624037\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n        \r\n</figure></div>\n<div>垃圾桶、书报亭、自行车、花束，甚至一只鸽子都被染上了明亮的黄色涂层。<br>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105020WcHGUkh4i7lvtTQX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105020ZJP801qS3xEDHbhv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105021g13RZfi5xsrjScU2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7171875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Purdy 位于纽约的户外广告</p></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p>Purdy 用这种方式展示 Purdy XL 刷可以随心所欲地在砖、玻璃、木材、金属和塑料等任何表面上涂画。</p>\n<div>另一面广告墙为了展示 Purdy Clearcut 系列的油漆精确度，在墙面砖的缝隙间涂漆。 </div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105022u5pSNtnslgmqPAWC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105022xnZATdR0i6kyPOsq.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Purdy 位于克利夫兰的广告墙</p>\n<p>          </p></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div>涂料广告并不都是那么好看，大多数时候我们看到的是这样的。 </div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105022425IzeOobltCkRN8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60729167\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure></div>\n<div>德国连锁家装 OBI 就曾经反思了这一点：广告明明是为了推广让世界更美的产品，可为什么广告本身会让世界如此丑陋呢？</div>\n<p>于是他们挑选了城市中的危房旧楼，好好装点了一番。 </p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105023wkhr38EKPfHyiI1n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105023p7FWU4fBajdZ8GbI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5515625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071050241W2zqmENnZy7kOXv.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105024jfIkxamLKwqoeunO.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060710502568mFwEurCWP9bO1h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.646875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure></div>\n<div>\n<span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial;\">在一片破败的迹象中，鲜亮的广告牌一角写着 “Renovated with OBI” (由 OBI 翻新)。</span><br>\n</div>\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial;\">这样的广告是不是既抢眼，又不招人厌呢？</span></p>\n\n\n\n"}